<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Sans+KR:wght@200;300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
        <title>Esqueceu a Senha</title>

        <style>
            * {
                border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;
                font-family: 'Hind Siliguri', sans-serif;
            }

            body {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                background-color: white;
                width: 100vw;
                height: auto;
                padding-top: 15px;
                line-height: 20px;
            }

            #fp-template {
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                width: 400px;
                height: auto;
            }

            #div-dont-reply {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                width: 100%;
                padding: 15px;
                background-color: white;
            }

            #dont-reply {
                padding: 5px 0px;
                font-size: 14px;
                font-style: italic;
                font-family: initial;
            }

            #inner-box {
                background-color: #1C2B3A;
                border: 1px solid rgb(180, 179, 179);
                border-radius: 7px;
            }

            header {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                width: 100%;
                padding: 15px 0px;
            }

            #logo {
                height: 75px;
                width: auto;
                transform: translateX(22px);
            }

            #fp-div-title {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                width: 100%;
            }

            #fp-title {
                color: lightsteelblue;
                font-size: 20px;
                padding: 5px 15px;
            }

            #fp-greeting {
                color: #1C2B3A;
                font-size: 20px;
                padding: 10px 0px 20px 0px;
                font-style: italic;
            }

            #fp-content {
                background-color: whitesmoke;
                font-size: 16px;
                padding: 20px;
                color: rgb(90, 89, 89);
            }

            #fp-orientation p {
                display: inline;
                line-height: 20px;
            }

            #key-pass{
                color: rgb(248, 110, 60);
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            #grp-fp-button {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                margin: 5px 0px;
                padding-left: 100px;
            }

            #btn-fp {
                height: 35px;
                width: 160px;
                margin: 20px 0px;
            }

            #fp-attention {
                text-align: justify;
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            #fp-regards {
                margin-top: 20px;
                line-height: 25px;
                font-style: italic;
            }

            .buttons{
                color: white;
                height: 35px;
                width: 100px;
                border-radius: 7px;
                font-size: 14px;
                font-weight: 700;
                margin: 0px 10px;
                cursor: pointer;
            }

            .button-fp{
                background-color:#F0AB3E;
            }

            #footer-bar {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: left;
                width: 100%;
                padding: 15px;
            }

        </style>
    </head>

    <body>
        <div id="fp-template">        
            <div id="fp-wrapper">
                <div id="div-dont-reply">
                    <p id='dont-reply'>**Esse é um email automático. Por favor, não responda.**</p>
                </div>
                <div id="inner-box">
                    <header>
                        <div id='fp-div-logo'>
                            <img id='logo' src="/img/logo.png" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <div id='fp-div-title'>
                            <p id='fp-title'>Redefinição de Senha</p>
                        </div>
                    </header>
                    <div id='fp-content'>
                        <p id="fp-greeting">Olá, <%= user.firstName %>!</p>
                        <div id='fp-orientation'>
                            <p>Para redefinir da sua senha, clique no botão abaixo e utilize o código:</p>
                            <p id='key-pass'><%= user.senha %></p>
                        </div>
                        <div id="grp-fp-button">
                            <a href="http://localhost:3000/change-password"><button id="btn-fp" class="button-fp buttons">Redefinir Senha</button></a>
                        </div>    
                            
                        <div id='fp-attention'>Caso não tenha solicitado a redefinição da senha, aconselhamos seguir com a alteração como medida de segurança.</div>

                        <div id="fp-regards">
                            <p>Atenciosamente, </p>
                            <p>Equipe Acesso Nerd</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div id="footer-bar"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>